@startuml UC07_Sequence
title UC07: 查看成绩 - 顺序图

actor "学生" as Student
boundary "成绩查询页面" as GradePage
control "成绩控制类" as GradeCtrl
entity "Grade" as Grade

Student -> GradePage : 进入页面
GradePage -> GradeCtrl : getGrades(studentId)
GradeCtrl -> Grade : findByStudent(studentId)
Grade --> GradeCtrl : gradeDataList

GradeCtrl -> GradeCtrl : calculateStatistics(gradeDataList)
GradeCtrl --> GradePage : 返回成绩列表及统计分析图表
GradePage -> Student : 展示详情
@enduml
